title: La Vieille Dame Indigne 1965 WEB-DL Sonata Premiere
description:
A sixty-something woman became a widow. All her life, she had been cooking, washing and taking care of her family. A woman's work is never done. So she decided she would live for herself: she would go to the pictures, she would buy a car and that's exactly what she did. Bertold Brecht told us so: She had two lives: the first one was a long busy one, the second one was very short; but she ate the bread of life till its last crumbs.
